{"readme":"<h1 class=\"title\"><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://github.com/stackgl/glsl-perturb-normal\">glsl-perturb-normal</a><div class=\"contrib\"></div></h1>\n<p><a href=\"http://github.com/badges/stability-badges\"></a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/RCn9tjK.jpg\" alt=\"demo-image\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://stack.gl/glsl-perturb-normal/demo\">(click for demo)</a></p>\n<!-- iframe: http://stack.gl/glsl-perturb-normal/demo -->\n<p>Perturb a normal in the fragment shader using a normal map. This can be used to add surface detail during per-pixel lighting. </p>\n<p><em>Note:</em> You need to enable <code>GL_OES_standard_derivatives</code>.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"lang-glsl\"><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span>#extension&#xA0;GL_OES_standard_derivatives&#xA0;:&#xA0;enable</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"storage modifier glsl\"><span>varying</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>vec3</span></span><span>&#xA0;vNormal;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"storage modifier glsl\"><span>varying</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>vec2</span></span><span>&#xA0;vUv;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"storage modifier glsl\"><span>varying</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>vec3</span></span><span>&#xA0;vViewPosition;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"storage modifier glsl\"><span>uniform</span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>sampler2D</span></span><span>&#xA0;normalMap;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span>#</span><span class=\"meta preprocessor keyword import define glsl\"><span>pragma&#xA0;glslify:</span></span><span class=\"entity name function glsl\"><span>&#xA0;perturb&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"operator glsl\"><span>=&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"keyword operator glsl\"><span>require</span></span><span>(</span><span class=\"string quoted double\"><span>&apos;glsl-perturb-normal&apos;</span></span><span>)</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>void</span></span><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace function leading c\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"entity name function c\"><span>main</span></span><span class=\"meta parens c\"><span class=\"punctuation section parens begin c\"><span>(</span></span><span class=\"punctuation section parens end c\"><span>)</span></span></span><span>&#xA0;</span><span class=\"meta block c\"><span class=\"punctuation section block begin c\"><span>{</span></span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace comment leading c++\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"comment line double-slash c++\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment c++\"><span>//</span></span><span>extract&#xA0;normal&#xA0;map&#xA0;from&#xA0;your&#xA0;texture</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>vec3</span></span><span>&#xA0;normalRGB&#xA0;=</span><span class=\"meta function-call c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace function-call leading c\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"support function any-method c\"><span>texture2D</span></span><span>(</span></span><span>normalMap,&#xA0;vUv)</span><span class=\"punctuation separator variable-access c\"><span>.</span></span><span class=\"variable other dot-access c\"><span>rgb</span></span><span>;</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace comment leading c++\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"comment line double-slash c++\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment c++\"><span>//</span></span><span>expand&#xA0;into&#xA0;-1.0&#xA0;..&#xA0;1.0&#xA0;range</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>vec3</span></span><span>&#xA0;normalMap&#xA0;=&#xA0;normalRGB&#xA0;*&#xA0;</span><span class=\"constant numeric c\"><span>2.0</span></span><span>&#xA0;-&#xA0;</span><span class=\"constant numeric c\"><span>1.0</span></span><span>;</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace comment leading c++\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"comment line double-slash c++\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment c++\"><span>//</span></span><span>get&#xA0;surface&#xA0;normal&#xA0;and&#xA0;camera-space&#xA0;position</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>vec3</span></span><span>&#xA0;N&#xA0;=</span><span class=\"meta function-call c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace function-call leading c\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"support function any-method c\"><span>normalize</span></span><span>(</span></span><span>vNormal);</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>vec3</span></span><span>&#xA0;V&#xA0;=</span><span class=\"meta function-call c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace function-call leading c\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"support function any-method c\"><span>normalize</span></span><span>(</span></span><span>vViewPosition);</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace comment leading c++\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"comment line double-slash c++\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment c++\"><span>//</span></span><span>perturb&#xA0;the&#xA0;normal</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span><span class=\"storage type glsl\"><span>vec3</span></span><span>&#xA0;normal&#xA0;=</span><span class=\"meta function-call c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace function-call leading c\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"support function any-method c\"><span>perturb</span></span><span>(</span></span><span>normalMap,&#xA0;N,&#xA0;V,&#xA0;vUv);</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span class=\"punctuation whitespace comment leading c++\"><span>&#xA0;&#xA0;</span></span><span class=\"comment line double-slash c++\"><span class=\"punctuation definition comment c++\"><span>//</span></span><span>...&#xA0;lighting</span><span>&#xA0;</span></span></span></span></span></div><div class=\"line\"><span class=\"source glsl\"><span class=\"meta function c\"><span class=\"meta block c\"><span class=\"punctuation section block end c\"><span>}</span></span></span></span></span></div>\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://nodei.co/npm/glsl-perturb-normal/\"></a></p>\n<h4 id=\"vec3-perturbed-perturb-vec3-m-vec3-n-vec3-v-vec2-texcoord-\"><code>vec3 perturbed = perturb(vec3 M, vec3 N, vec3 V, vec2 texcoord)</code></h4>\n<p>Perturbs a normal where:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>M</code> is a unit vector from your normal map (e.g. decoded from a RGB texture)</li>\n<li><code>N</code> is the normalized surface normal</li>\n<li><code>V</code> is the normalized camera-space position</li>\n<li><code>texcoord</code> is the UV coordinates of your mesh</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This uses <code>GL_OES_standard_derivatives</code> to compute the derivatives, so it may not work on older or low-end devices. </p>\n<h2 id=\"credits\">Credits</h2>\n<p>The algorithm here is from Chris&#xAD;t&#xAD;ian Sch&#xFC;ler&apos;s blog post <a href=\"http://www.thetenthplanet.de/archives/1180\">Normal Mapping Without Precomputed Tangents</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"license\">License</h2>\n<p>MIT. See <a href=\"http://github.com/stackgl/glsl-perturb-normal/blob/master/LICENSE.md\">LICENSE.md</a> for details.</p>\n"}